column5: to the first person who tells me what dates it is on!!  Only reply if you can go, as tickets will be picked up at the will-call booth.
If the Mrs and kids don't want to go then you can come with me.
Nice going Geoff (assuming you are the winner) Which day are we going?
don't know about you but I'm going when Mercer is going to be speaking.
There ya go GBW.... pm me your address etc so I can put ya on the list!
Ah the list.Hold yer head high.Congrats.
HAHAHA, good to know, or do I know
change of plans... So, when is Pete speaking?  That's when I'm going to go.
Geoff, email Pete. He'll tell you everything you want to know.
another change of plans...  I cannot go give the tickets to Sinclair please.  Cheers. Geoff
